data.description: Experience luxury in the exclusive Polo Grounds at Pointe West Community with this custom-built pool home. This 3-bed, 3-bath residence boasts high-quality finishes, upgrades, and recent updates throughout its expansive 3000 sq ft floor plan, all situated on a meticulously landscaped 1/2 acre lot. The home features a 2022 roof and newer A/C units, as detailed in the feature sheet provided in the photos.  Enjoy the unique advantage of Polo matches visible from your front yard, or unwind by the pool while witnessing Polo horses in action on the practice field just beyond your pond. With unobstructed front and back views of open pastures that cannot be developed, this property offers a serene retreat. A short golf cart ride away from Pointe West Country Club. Immerse yourself in the epitome of upscale living in this Polo Grounds residence.
